{
  "2141990": {
    "name": "魔塔三国之逆乱时空",
    "steam_appid": 2141990,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎关注微信公众号“抓狗离”</h2>公众号历史文章会持续更新游戏攻略，可以加入我们的游戏群与其他玩家一起讨论怎么打，以及看到其他我们制作的游戏<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >本游戏为三国背景的开放式rpg游戏</h2>玩家在随机界面随机出一个角色后开始游戏，<br>玩家成长游戏中的后期可以吃成长丹药<br>角色资质在重生后获得潜力，通过使用资质丹进行提升（游戏中最多重生10第四章开始每章解锁两次）<br>角色特性会跟着角色等级提升而解锁（可在游戏通过八章收集龙龙珠后跟神龙许愿进行替换）<br>左侧各类开局需要进行游戏达成一定的完成度后解锁。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/21939a103818beb54918269e94bb28e2.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=344 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/6115b03877edf72eca10e1dc5313fb5b.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=330 /></span><br>图中举世无双资质为玩家“嫩牛🥩 五方”投稿<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏概述</h2>玩家通过完成主线任务推进游戏的时代历程，召集队友，打怪升级，锻造装备，学习技能，等队伍足够强大了再去攻城掠地，统一天下。<br>进而挑战最终神仙boss拯救迷失在时空乱流中的晋穿。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >世界地图缩略</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/d3379400f773192eda06095d077e6b34.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=511 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/76ce02169eb6bf757e2482b24186046d.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=475 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/589ad7ada014bb3ed09d36e634e76f01.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=481 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/41afa59eae7b4e383c1713591a4b6dc0.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=568 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/52cbe55171650a6516568ebc34ba5600.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=402 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/a8fc95a291d8f687d2479ddd707f1076.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=602 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/692fbd14a0f7ca5ef780ad89cfed2cdd.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=611 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/9b0064b7bd2d6dd69009b71763e8dbeb.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=510 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/3c3cdf8a2d6fbdf401dae53ce0df90d5.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=648 /></span><br>地形说明（游戏中右侧的内置攻略中可以查看详细）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/c5c18a0d360f944ce80e8069473d7c90.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=388 /></span><br>按右侧的地图按钮可以使用传送功能<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/48027fa346852e2d14301677dcb30e25.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>点击全国地图选择不同的州郡可以进入二级城市传送<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/0ce92584564c9a6aedb58b385ce80f62.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>点击返回基地可以返回基地地图，基地多家商店购买装备<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/598a22de4082fdda939a692457878a48.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=452 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基地建筑</h2>药庐（道具店），可以买到丹药（角色成长丹，升级经验丹，角色资质丹，金色角色丹（概率极低）），招募令 刷新需要消耗道具刷新券（全部刷新券由完成主线任务和支线任务获得，战斗小概率获得）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/a57c648c2082c15ea183e6b7fa241ff4.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/22230b60666ae407aa31cee3d907208a.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>辎重（粮店），可以买入兵粮，卖出多余资源<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/bd8f089927297b410fbf4eccd14238de.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/0cbaab9b874066dc0e5818ad07cb9cba.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>学宫（技能店），可以买到符合当前队伍中角色的技能书（超神级技能书不会出现）需要技能店刷新券刷新<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/d8a5959d9713d6ae48020e2ebe34e4c3.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/c26136cdba337e636078f56d79e91999.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>铁匠（锻造店），可以锻造加强武器，给武器附魔，洗炼仙山武器<br>（概率提高装备属性仙山武器的上限分别是圣：900，仙：2000 神：4000 混沌：9000）<br>（上限的概念为武器属性总和数）（每个武器的上限是不一定的掉落的时候就决定了多少上限）<br>圣：在玄霄青玉洞打历史名将掉落<br>仙：在斜月三星洞打仙人掉落<br>神：在九天真王宫打仙人掉落<br>混沌：在鸿蒙幻境打五圣掉落<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/9767bafcb1bc4b4211851c75d76b50b2.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/4d27fe175fd5e259f1b63df1d7fb2501.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>酒肆（治疗店），10块恢复全队血量和怒气<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/d272f68a8d42e0446420b7ce515823c6.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/1cb918b8e4b5c6706c622be9ed6374a9.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>兵器（装备店），只会刷新出现在当前上阵队员能穿着的装备，<br>神话装备不要求级别其他成长级别的武器会要求等级<br>只会刷新到专属武器这一个级别。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/1673db239ac4ea0974510b92071b2a69.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/0359e574f038dc06478150bd02a5070e.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>裁缝（形象转换），在店里可以花钱更换角色的形象。<br>左侧为更改战斗页面的形象，右侧为更改地图里的形象<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/fe7c69234ac657cfda6c8abedc5f1183.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/9fac5d5421dd3475021f601b178144a9.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >操作介绍</h2>战斗界面<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/1188c79f89584c441bbb02d0ff1dbff3.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>我方为左边，对方的出场人数按照我方出场人数相等<br>下方攻击为普通攻击，点下选定一个对方角色<br>技能为当前角色的技能表，其中红色的为之前习得的技能但是不适用于现在的职业<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/d8e47529c18cb388d8d0121ec39b8ef5.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>调查中看到紫色的技能为自动释放的技能，一次手动操作后会记录使用了哪个技能，使用招募会重置默认技能需要再次手动选择一次<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/5607dbd092f82a026172406744692e20.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>点击调查再点击武将可以看到其详细面板<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/e31546aedf6150542bf477ef33cd87e0.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>点击招募再点击对象武将，呼出招募令列表（越高级的招募令概率上招募成功率越高）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/371b2f643194b65656f86a7cfe8c3721.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>点击撤退会进行逃跑拥有疾跑特性的武将逃跑概率会提高（部分敌方武将会发起逃跑，需要你速度超过他并且在他们逃跑前控制他或者弄死他）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/b52f2b27bcd56ae3c32760b9cf2ee942.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>点击返回会回到上一个角色的操作界面<br>行动页面<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/669e27cd988f451e172ec15279ff1236.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>左侧的任务按钮可以在当前状态和当前主线任务之间切换<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/9bfff3e2b65cb80878d45513defc45a2.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>主线任务为拖进游戏进程的判定依据（完成主线任务会接到龙珠任务击杀特定角色获得一颗龙珠）<br>当前状态<br>依次显示剧本：当前所在的时代<br>中间省略<br>所在城市_所在地形 当前地图的X轴位置，当前地图的y轴位置<br>任务面板<br>任务目标人物<br>所在的时代（如果你在某个城市找不到对应的人先看看是不是所在的时代没有对上）<br>所在的城市_所在的城市下属地形<br>奖励预览<br>（如果当前完成了任务点击信息/完成 会完成该任务并且刷新下一个主线任务的内容）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/c786b6341fdb6ff0ade0717ee6bae617.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>右侧点击主页面会回到登录选择新游戏和继续游戏的页面<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/d63691a3158048df89d18789c29bdb51.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>地图可以呼出快速传送和返回基地<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/48027fa346852e2d14301677dcb30e25.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>声音开关切换<br>游戏存档，包括一个切换场景或者进入战斗进行自动存档的自动挡<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/4e35d6f182b46ba4f9c1e3d9e1329e01.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>仓库页面（一键完成任务可以完成主线以及支线任务，清仓会卖出全部未锁定的物品，商人的自动贩卖从第一个未锁定物品卖出，一次卖出全部这个格子里的物品）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/440008e5e356ac57052029f12e13f154.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>使用兵粮，恢复上阵角色的全部血量<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/d625cc85a4750abf276f6475a0129ce5.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>队伍调整下阵当前队员，上阵替补队员，以及遣散未被锁定的队员（通常是遣散拥有丹精·？的队员以获得资质丹）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/5a5547511a017d009d234feb8964164d.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>情报页面可以查看当前的游戏进度（steam中进度将会解锁不同的开局按钮）<br>以及查看玩家完成的游戏收集图鉴<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/52a88a327b22faa13effe203045efb1c.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>其中游戏百科一项在游戏里可以直接查询你需要查询的职业人物特性技能（注意大小写和繁简体）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/3fbc2f3f5f499eab5f7d4b8ef7bab364.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>内置攻略集成了游戏的各类简介<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/e933ecfb51b1692c7af378fa3170eaf9.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >海外仙山副本</h2>根据上一代魔塔三国之群雄争霸的玩家建议<br>把武器和特性让玩家自由组合<br>这一代推出了仙山副本系统<br>在海外打神兽获得附魔丹，洞府打神仙和名将获得高基础值装备，二者合一而获得极品装备。<br>仙岛可以在特定时代解锁之后的海上找到入口<br>也可以由主基地传送<br>（建议用主基地传送门，比如你已经解锁了蓬莱仙山，在第六章的海上也能进入但是第六章的蓬莱没有配置怪物，于是什么怪都找不到）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/598a22de4082fdda939a692457878a48.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=452 /></span><br>瀛洲仙山在第三章飞将乱舞解锁进入（基地主城左下传送门）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/8511c70e99ee4985acf09f4363dc1feb.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=416 /></span><br>玄霄青玉洞在第四章官渡之战解锁进入（基地主城右下传送门）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/cc480179d2ef122137584d8ef33d6976.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=529 /></span><br>方寸仙山在第五章赤壁之战解锁进入（基地主城左中传送门）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/e94c393ca54f8e0244c37c1168afe5c0.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=416 /></span><br>斜月三星洞在第六章三足鼎立解锁进入（基地主城右中传送门）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/9b1c8c0a1f8f0600bc5ca8d6ec094fc1.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=528 /></span><br>蓬莱仙山在第七章六出祁山解锁进入（基地主城左上传送门）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/b7d90ff2c56792619df20577b306bafc.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=416 /></span><br>九天真王宫在第八章三分归晋解锁进入（基地主城右上传送门）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/df4e26c265a6fb94ea97ce461e736ec7.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=545 /></span><br>仙山掉落表公众号文章链接<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >技能篇</h2>此版本的技能按照角色的职业进行匹配 需要该角色的职业能学习且等级达到该技能的要求<br>技能公众号汇总文章链接<br>此外在游戏右侧按钮情报弹出界面游戏百科中搜索<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/5ffa9ef1ccf2e13ee64a204e8bef1268.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >被动特性</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/c26fcf490165a14da38088e50b50d90d.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>现行被动表公众号文章链接<br>一个角色身上最多可以有：角色4个特性，职业4个特性，装备5个特性，核心1个特性<br>角色特性按照角色的等级解锁，开局选定角色显示的自身特性需要通过升级进行解锁<br>（吃了重生丹后等级为1，这就需要玩家再次升级解锁特性）<br>（角色特性可以在龙珠许愿处获得愿望“我要火”进行变更为四红）<br>职业特性会跟着你职业进阶而发生变化<br>转职需要职业凭证，（掉落凭证需要练兵特性，不同等级的练兵能掉落的职业凭证阶段不同，详见上方的被动表文章，初始在第二章右边的海上抓一个儒将）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/163eebd40082415b6b12cab600cef9f2.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>装备特性可以通过给装备附魔不同的附魔丹而变化<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/a2905c365596bb2bac6a2c22d7214925.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>附魔丹掉落于仙山副本<br>掉落表见 仙山掉落表公众号文章链接<br>核心特性可以使用武魂<br>武魂来自于和武将战斗时掉落（需要超度系的特性，不同等级的超度能掉落的武魂星级不同详，见上方的被动表文章，初始可以去北边地形-雪林抓个和尚）<br>游戏开始阶段只能掉落一次，后续可以使用龙珠许愿“重复掉落武魂”，即可重复获得武魂<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/0e47fdfedcc8bf795b75cad99c3d06b0.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/051dae481f4764bf8557db26ce74ab62.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >职业篇</h2>不同的职业有着不一样的属性修正，可用装备，地形修正<br>详细见公众号文章<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >龙珠篇</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/32272c0f477efb12430dfd61749bbc70.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>玩家需要挑战每一个时代的城池获得龙珠之尘<br>（前期打不过不要执着（咱也打不过（第一章尤其是刘关张在的蓟）），先做主线任务去后面的时代，之后再回头来打就是了）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/bbedc3c1ce55a2e203a4a3e1987aedf1.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>打完一个时代49座城市后可以合成一个龙珠<br>（带着肝帝特性的角色去打城市给的经验很多的）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/0e7271e7166a807e32115c24fd0f7862.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>集齐八个龙珠后可以向基地神龙许愿<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/b0359784ea22299e2c23f758ed77376c.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/d3d3e1734aad111d593750f80ff6ba9e.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>许愿后会获得一个愿望在仓库里点击使用<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/7a275e4660d2e5d90f1d6eafc120f4ae.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>建议第一个愿望选择“商店内刷新龙珠”<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >经常收到反映的吕布怎么过的问题</h2>据通关大佬的打法投稿，基地左侧的第一个传送门，<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/6b7ac45bc271d960c3c09b0b37179325.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>进入瀛洲仙山，找金羽刷练兵LV4。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/e7439bb0afb3d056491ff72996c18656.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/1d0fc33a05dd3b9f91fc5a41473cf528.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/23a5a6b802f3f661bdfa0687585303ba.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>获得练兵LV4后回基地铁匠铺后堂早到附魔工匠<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/4d27fe175fd5e259f1b63df1d7fb2501.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>随意物品附魔练兵LV4（这里我选择了一个宝物位的物品方便全职业通用）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/a2905c365596bb2bac6a2c22d7214925.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>再去抓一个神弓骑的前置职业轻骑兵（点击情报按钮-游戏百科输入要搜索的职业，人物，特性，技能都能列出游戏内的详细说明）<br>其中绿色的字体可以快速跳转到该词条<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/bae35d4d57e38360068b4e863ea2b329.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/6036dde4275b8683d37102e1188ae5ff.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/60fa475aca7ce71bfbb83439f588ae4b.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>找对应的武将刷职业证明（自选武将一个上阵带附魔练兵LV4对方就一个张任的神弓骑证书掉落概率会比较高）<br>再去第二章董卓进京-雪地抓一个资质好点的神弓骑（最好有毒王特性，没有也可以用）让他使用神弓骑证转职成神弓骑<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/eef6555ccf61ad0a3d2d25bc8628d7b9.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>调整队伍只留下主角和神弓骑去技能店刷技能书（技能店只会刷出你当前队伍中的职业能用的技能书（超神级技能书不会出现在商店中））<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/b890013df72704ed6899d54b167c0f24.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>刷这个“九空神箭”技能，给转职成神弓骑的角色学<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/9de76c70192c79d1c3076fb466a0593c.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>再去下邳神弓骑使用“九空神箭”（因为该技能有速度修正所以会比吕布快）带几个铁甲兵来抗揍活到吕布被毒死即可<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141990/extras/1ca5f0e2102f6910053cef2d576bd91c.avif?t=1666709835\" width=620 height=286 /></span><br>如果扛不住吕布去打钱升级一下防具（铁甲兵出现地形在本章节飞将乱舞-林）<br>此描述还不是完整版还会继续更新，反映多的地方攻略会持续更新。<br>如果你曾经玩过fc版本的吞食天地系列，或者对三国背景游戏特别青睐，本游戏必定会给你一段不一样的体验。",
